data.text: @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe You sure did make us proud in your Fan Club Hype people groups by singing our National Anthem...it made me tingle to hear it done Maddie Poppe’s Way! 🇺🇸❤️🎶
@CindyISU87 @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Anyone outside of a 30 mile radius usually pronounces it that way - it's spelled the same as the city overseas, in Egypt?  I think
@TeresaPowers6 @ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Bummer! But there are so many clips out there!
@ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe A lot of people say  TripoLIE, but I didn't think that was right! Now I know for sure!

@CindyISU87 @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe ok, will do my best on the pronunciation    -  Tri (short "i")   Po' (accent on this syllable with long 'o' )   Li  (short 'i')     But very few people know how to pronounce it..
@CindyISU87 @ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Wrong day to schedule my car to be in the shop!!! Wah!!
@IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe I know this guy! And so bummed I missed this morning! Ya gonna be at Eastsude nite?? 😂 #IowaLovesMaddie and Caleb too! https://t.co/2tMw7FAheg

@ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe I hate Iowa winters!!! I've heard of all the towns you've mentioned and been to some of them! :) I've always wondered the correct pronunciation of Tripoli. Can you help me out? :)

@CindyISU87 @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Have family in Cedar Rapids, Waterloo, Oelwein, Tripoli, Plainfield and a brother near you in Waukee - I try to avoid coming up in the winter, don't like all that white stuff very much!

@CindyISU87 @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Ok, hope this isn't a repeat of my reply - I'm not very computer savvy, but I don't think the first replay came through.  I've been in Texas since 1958, so have given away my age,   but I still get up to Iowa at least once a year, sometimes more.
@ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe I sure have! Our school (Colo-Nesco) plays Tripoli in sports now.
@CindyISU87 @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Bet you've heard of it   - Tripoli

@ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Which town in Iowa by Clarksville? I lived in Clarksville the first year of my life! My dad taught high school math there for a year.

@ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe No, no, no - not Iowa City! lol I live about 30 miles from Ames and Iowa State! '87 alum and met my husband there! Go Cyclones! 😀❤️💛
@PoppeTravels @CindyISU87 @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Are you in Iowa City Cindy?  I see the ISU behind your name
@ruthiebsmith @CindyISU87 @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Yes, she flew to Tulsa to meet up with the other Idols!

@CindyISU87 @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe I bet she' ll fly, it's only about a 45 min flight from DSM to KC  - I'm originally from Iowa, a town only about 30 miles from her home town, so get up that way fairly often since I still have family there - I know she'll be happy to get back to Iowa , if even for a short time.
@IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Take lots of photos

@ruthiebsmith @PoppeTravels @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Yes, she won't have time to hang out at the fair all day! It's about a 3 hour drive from Des Moines to KC, unless she flies. Still such a cool thing to happen!
@PoppeTravels @CindyISU87 @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe It'll be a quick trip if she is, Idol tour is in Tulsa tonite, and KC tomorrow night, on the 9th
@CindyISU87 @ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Yes she will be “home “ for this honor!! ❤️🎶
@ChrisSauke @IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe According to https://t.co/eGJLyS2uFV Channel 5 news in Des Moines she will be there.
@IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Congrats Maddie! So nice to see the Iowan support...there’s no place like home ❤️🎶
@IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Congrats Maddie
@IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe @IowaStateFair Will she be there?
@IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe This means @MaddiePoppe will be there???
@IowaStateFair @MaddiePoppe Great news, very deserving.
